message: "If you use or reference IREP, please cite it as below."
title: "IREP — Individual-Referential Evaluation Protocol"
abstract: "A free, open, non-proprietary and not-for-sale protocol (available to commercial and non-commercial implementers alike) for hiring and admissions: category-blind, trajectory-rich evaluation first; demographic and administrative measurement after the decision, firewalled, for audit only. The individual is the reference class; the population is the audit instrument."
type: software
authors:
